lead_paragraph: Zach Auguste had 21 points and 12 rebounds and Demetrius Jackson added 14 points in his return as No. 25 Notre Dame defeated Wake Forest 85-62 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Jackson, Auguste Lead No. 25 Notre Dame Over Wake 85-62
